Name: Yuuki's Party Night
About the game: A short fun visual novel, following Yuuki as she goes on her first night out for a long time, to an outdoor costume party no less. Will Yuuki meet a new friend or find someone special in her life? Or simply have one hell of a night?! It is up to you as you make key decisions in this multi route visual novel. Features - Visual Novel Style Gameplay - Multiple Decision to Make - Secret Lingerie Outfit to Unlock - Beautiful & Sexy Illustrations * All characters included in the game are at least 18 years of age.
